name: LastmileProbeResultState
description: The status of the last-mile network tests.

parameters.Complete: 1: The last-mile network probe test is complete.

parameters.IncompleteNoBwe: 2: The last-mile network probe test is incomplete because the bandwidth estimation is not available due to limited test resources.

parameters.Unavailable: 3: The last-mile network probe test is not carried out, probably due to poor network conditions.
